# Normalize all text files to LF in the repository and on checkout. This
# avoids the CRLF/LF churn that's been showing previously-committed files
# (e.g. README.md, package.json, page.tsx files) as perpetually "modified"
# on Windows even with no real content change — eol=lf forces a consistent
# line ending on checkout instead of letting core.autocrlf convert back and
# forth, which is what caused files to end up with mixed line endings after
# edits.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary files — never touch line endings, never diff as text.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.eot binary
